+  projection, Calderon-Zygmund, commutator, and Biot-Savart debt charged
+  explicitly.
+- Label claims as `[VERIFIED]`, `[INFERRED]`, or `[PROPOSED]`.
+- Record dead ends and failed attempts honestly.
