+- [PROPOSED] `divergence / stress form` may only move derivatives onto the
+  cutoff and then recreate the same stress-against-`nabla phi` burden after
+  integration by parts.
+- [PROPOSED] `Lamb-vector / Helmholtz-projected form` may expose a cleaner
+  first-order identity, but any gain may disappear once projection / pressure /
+  commutator debt is restored after localization.
+
+## Dead Ends / Rejected Paths
+
+- None yet.
+
+## Provisional Conclusion
+
+- Pending source review.

