/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:28:- The step assumes there is a clean "averaged-model counterpart at the same level of description." That is not automatic. Tao's averaged equation is not just "NS with slightly modified triad coefficients." The comparison can become representation-dependent and technically slippery.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:29:- Even if one writes down different helical or triad coefficients, coefficient-level nonidentity is cheap. The relevant question is whether the difference produces a sign, monotonicity, forbidden transfer, or quantitatively stronger cancellation after summing over all admissible configurations. The step does not force that distinction sharply enough.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:30:- "Isolate what averaging preserves and what it destroys" is necessary but insufficient. Averaging can destroy exact geometry while preserving enough effective interaction strength that no regularity leverage remains. The chain risks mistaking "not identical" for "operationally distinguishable."
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:31:- The kill condition uses "same effective strength," but effective strength is undefined. Is that pointwise in the symbol? averaged over orientations? after frequency summation? after localization? after time averaging? Without that definition, the gate can be passed or failed by rhetoric.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:40:- The instruction to reject "identity-level curiosity" is good in spirit, but the chain still lacks an objective test for that rejection. Without a fixed downstream estimate, this will be a subjective screening step dressed up as rigor.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:70:The chain treats "exact NS triad geometry differs from Tao-averaged geometry" as though this is already close to a breakthrough criterion. It is not. The missing ingredient is a mechanism that survives summation, localization, and dynamics. The chain acknowledges this only late.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:72:### 2. It is too close to harmonic-analysis territory to feel safely beyond Tao
