+### 3. Candidate: `Lamb-vector / Helmholtz-projected form`
+
+- [INFERRED] Exact claimed Navier-Stokes feature:
+  isolate the gradient piece in
+  `(u · ∇)u = ∇(|u|^2/2) - u × omega`,
